<P>
 COACH: RECORD AT SCHOOL Eric Patton: 48-20-2 03,20,05,05 RETURNING STARTERS 
OFF DEF 1 1 04,28,05,05,05 TOP RETURNERS OFF DEF YR Jeff Brion, 5-10, 180 -- DB 
Sr. Ben Conrad, 6-2, 180 -- DB Sr. Chris Culbertson, 6-2, 190 -- LB Jr. Tim 
Englehardt, 6-3, 220 OL -- Sr. Paul Fulbright, 6-3, 225 -- LB Sr. Kurt Grigas, 
5-11, 195 RB LB Sr. Chris Honeycutt, 6-0, 260 OL -- Sr. Andrew Klein, 5-11, 200 
-- DL Sr. Jason Purvis, 6-5, 210 TE -- Sr. Jamie Thomson, 5-10, 220 OL -- Sr. 
B.J. Williams, 5-11, 235 OL -- Sr. 04,30,05,05,05 TOP NEWCOMERS OFF DEF YR 
Trent Aronson, 6-3, 200 -- DL Jr. Adrian Edwards, 5-7, 165 RB DB Sr. Tim 
Hirchag, 5-11, 170 QB -- So. Charlie Landrigan, 5-10, 190 RB -- So. Maleafou 
MacKenzie, 6-0, 190 RB -- So. Todd Miller, 5-7, 160 WR -- Jr. Dave Miner, 6-0, 
