 COACH: RECORD AT SCHOOL Bill Denny: 0-0 03,20,05,05 RETURNING STARTERS OFF DEF 
2 3 04,27,05,05,05 TOP RETURNERS OFF DEF YR Ryan Ballas, 5-9, 165 WR -- Sr. 
