 COACH: RECORD AT SCHOOL Mark McElroy: 13-8-1 03,20,05,05 RETURNING STARTERS 
OFF DEF 3 4 04,29,05,05,05 TOP RETURNERS OFF DEF YR Brad Baker, 6-2, 290 OL -- 
