From Associated Press 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Noblesse Six outran Darlin Sixarun and previously undefeated Major Rime in the 
$1.6-million All American Futurity on Monday. 
</P>
<P>
 Ridden by veteran jockey Chris Zamora of New Mexico, Noblesse Six took late 
command of the 440-yard sprint over the final 50 yards to earn the $1-million 
first prize. 
</P>
