<TEXT>
<P>
 The Ventura County Concert Band is seeking new musicians for the 1994-95 
concert season. 
</P>
<P>
 Openings are available in all band sections, including woodwinds, brass and 
percussion instruments.No auditions are required, but previous experience is 
necessary. 
