and kidnaping in connection with Loader's disappearance. Loader's car was found 
Thursday, the same day the bodies of William Brewer, 86, and Flossie Brewer, 
74, were found in their Fulton, Mo., home. The Brewers were robbed and each had 
been shot three times in the head, police said. The Brewers' car was found next 
near Oklahoma City alongside the body of 37-year-old Roxie Ruddel, who had been 
shot to death. Her pickup was missing, police said. 
