<DOCNO> LA090694-0153 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 076562 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
September 6, 1994, Tuesday, Valley Edition 
</P>
