 Juarez said the victim's companions found him about 10 feet under water about 
15 minutes after he waded in, Juarez said. 
</P>
<P>
 Paramedics airlifted Figueroa to Antelope Valley Hospital Medical Center where 
he died about 6:30 p.m. 
