$24,285 10.4 * California grants a teaching credential upon completion of 30 
units of graduate study and at least six months of student teaching. Most 
teachers enter at starting salary level, though the state allows districts to 
grant "emergency credentials" or hire people with just a bachelor's degree in 
some situations; those teachers typically make less than the salary shown 
above. 
</P>
<P>
 Sources: California Teachers' Assn.; Orange Service Center Council; individual 
districts  
</P>
<P>
 Researched by JODI WILGOREN/Los Angeles Times 
</P>
