<TEXT>
<P>
 TV series -- "Voyager," the latest installment of the "Star Trek" franchise 
starring Genevieve Bujold, will premiere on the new United/Paramount network in 
January. Friday's Morning Report mistakenly reported that the show is a 
syndicated series. 
